messages.message:
The mv command was giving this issue:
```owner@dev:~/instabase$ mv ~/.docker/config.json{,.bak} ~/.aws/config{,.bak}
mv: target '/home/owner/.aws/config.bak': No such file or directory```
Here's the updated command:
```mv ~/.docker/config.json{,.bak} && mv ~/.aws/config{,.bak} && mv ~/.aws/credentials{,.bak}```
